<section class="row justify-content-center text-center mb-5">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">About Loconotion</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            Loconotion is a lightweight, persistent note-taking application engineered for
            speed and reliability. Built on a Node.js and PostgreSQL stack, it bridges the
            gap between complex project management tools and simple text editors.
        </p>
        <hr class="my-4">
    </div>
</section>

<section class="row justify-content-center mb-5 text-center">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p class="lead">
            As Computer Scientists at CU Boulder, we
            recognized a need for a streamlined note taking environment that's distraction free,
            prioritizes data integrity and user-specific security. Loconotion provides
            a centralized hub for technical documentation, academic notes, and daily tasks.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

